<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Free Smart Tools</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

body{
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
margin:0;
text-align:center;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2);
color:white;
}

header{
font-size:40px;
font-weight:600;
padding:40px 20px;
}

.subtitle{
opacity:0.9;
margin-top:-20px;
}

.tools{
margin-top:40px;
}

.tool{
background:white;
color:black;
width:280px;
margin:20px;
padding:30px;
display:inline-block;
border-radius:15px;
box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
transition:0.3s;
}

.tool:hover{
transform:translateY(-10px);
}

.tool h2{
margin-top:0;
}

.btn{
text-decoration:none;
background:#667eea;
color:white;
padding:12px 25px;
border-radius:8px;
display:inline-block;
margin-top:10px;
}

.btn:hover{
background:#5563d1;
}

footer{
margin-top:60px;
padding:20px;
opacity:0.8;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
🚀 Free Smart Tools
<p class="subtitle">Fast • Free • Simple Online Tools</p>
</header>

<div class="tools">

<div class="tool">
<h2>📄 PDF to Word</h2>
<p>Convert PDF files to Word documents instantly.</p>
<a class="btn" href="pdf.html">Open Tool</a>
</div>

<div class="tool">
<h2>🖼 Screenshot Editor</h2>
<p>Edit screenshots, draw, crop and download.</p>
<a class="btn" href="editor.html">Open Tool</a>
</div>

<div class="tool">
<h2>🧮 Image Compressor</h2>
<p>Reduce image size without losing quality.</p>
<a class="btn" href="#">Coming Soon</a>
</div>

</div>

<footer>
© 2026 Free Smart Tools
</footer>

</body>
</html>
